# This folder keeps the run-time artefacts created by the agent:
#   - completed_courses.json  : durable checkpoint of finished courses
#   - course_run_summary.json : last structured run summary
#   - agent_run_<ts>.log      : full DEBUG log when --debug is on
#   - frame_diagnostics.jsonl : per-snapshot iframe/DOM diagnostics
# All contents are gitignored (see ../.gitignore) — only this .gitkeep is tracked.
